Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一次都沒成功過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去森林裡的話  邊走邊做記號比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很容易迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
